snippet.title: Lift Every Voice and Sing | Arr. Roland Carter
snippet.description:
Lift Every Voice and Sing with music by J. Rosamond Johnson, arranged by Roland Carter for SATB choirs with a piano accompaniment.

Lift Every Voice and Sing, often referred to as the "Black National Anthem" in the U.S., is arranged here by Roland Carter. Accessible vocal writing with a celebratory accompaniment makes this a great selection for honor choirs and festivals.

Purchase the music: https://www.giamusic.com/store/resource/lift-every-voice-and-sing-print-ww1880

#choral #lifteveryvoice #waltonmusic
